  A. User [ctb]
Maintainer: Reinhard Oldenburg <Reinhard.Oldenburg@math.uni-augsburg.de>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), nloptr
Description: The function CBregress performs a univariate linear regression according to the case based methodology. This typically results in better estimates than standard regression or orthogonal regression when both variables are measured with error. 
